Class ElevatorQueue

java.lang.Object
  ElevatorQueue
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable, Collection, Queue
public class ElevatorQueue
extends Object
implements Queue

This Queue is linked list that implements Queue. It also stores the floor number that the Elevator Queue sits on and the direction that it's passengers want to travel in. Some of the methods to make it implement Queue are left blank and are unusable.
